{"tid":2101013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好難照顧","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T13:07:20.000Z","uid":49847,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac2a97463d9e40cfc1193dc580775e7a69a1c2e","tid":2101013,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"由街頭抗爭 到今時今日 每日都係充滿住批鬥<br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭：<br />\n一開始批鬥汽油彈<br />\n捉鬼大賽<br />\n批鬥-0-0<br />\n<br />\n街頭抗爭開始減少<br />\n抗爭變成撐黃圈、立會、等外國出手<br />\n<br />\n每日一屌-黃圈：<br />\n人血饅頭<br />\n陳彥霖牆壁<br />\n黃店鬥黃店<br />\n龍門渣哥陸陸<br />\n<br />\n每日一屌-立會：<br />\n屌熱狗、屌泛民 OMDB 到今日屌何桂藍<br />\n<br />\n每日一屌-外國出手：<br />\n屌人討論移唔移民<br />\n移民？當97後condom 當40幾歲以上condom<br />\n當坐緊監手足condom<br />\n<br />\n由上年7-8月開始每日都離不開以上既野<br />\n<br />\n相反對家：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n團結到仆街<br />\n<br />\n唔好再怪乜鬼野PR五毛帶風向<br />\n自己諗下自己有冇份屌<br />\n<br />\n工又唔罷 乜都唔敢做 最敢就係抽絲剝繭出盡渾身解數去批鬥自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好真心問句 有幾多件藍絲同狗既批鬥輿論可以大過你地批鬥既自己人   <br />\n<br />\n係，呢到係討論區<br />\n但你同我都好明一樣野就係<br />\n一年365日都要睇住自己人點樣俾人批鬥<br />\n真係好撚失軍心<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">不過而家大家知都可能冇乜用 <br />\n批鬥已成習慣<br />\n大家都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0fcd88a13adf88f2671e3ca35984fbd9ee4a2b40","tid":2101013,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"開吹水台算<br />\n有緣睇到咪嗲兩句<br />\n好驚時事台班五毛大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c319aba388ac916d89a0444b179b2faf43ac5826","tid":2101013,"uid":54927,"like":0,"disli